Robert D. YOUNG, Claimant-Appellant, v. Anthony J. PRINCIPI, Secretary of Veterans Affairs, Respondent-Appellee. No. 02-7279. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. Oct. 19, 2004.

ON MOTION

ORDER

Upon consideration of Robert D. Young’s unopposed motion to voluntarily dismiss his appeal,

IT IS ORDERED THAT:

(1) The motion is granted.

(2) Each side shall bear its own costs.
